 class="xsl"><br></td></tr><tr><td class="number">1</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>the concurrent exercise by home rule units of powers and </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">2</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>functions exercised by the State. </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">3</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>For purposes of this Section "child abuse or neglect" </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">4</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>includes abuse or neglect of an adult resident as defined in </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">5</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>this Act. </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">6</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>(Source: P.A. 100-513, eff. 1-1-18; 100-1071, eff. 1-1-19</code><code>.)</code><code>
